<TR><TH>Not necesarily 90 mins<BR>
<I><FONT SIZE=-1>Posted 2000-01-04 22:10:22 by Angralad, Paladin of Lanys TVyl</FONT></I></TH></TR>
<TR><TD>While it is true we paladins get this once an Everquest Day this not always holds true.... you can &quot;cheat&quot; it, though not for YOUR benefit. In group situations LoH is one of the most important spells, if you're about to die but so is someone else, specially if he's more important than you are at the moment (say a healer or the party nuker or a strong tank) you can use it on him, save his but and then die happy, because even though dying really sucks youll have saved this your whole party probably AND when you re-spawn you'll have your LoH again available. In this way (not a nice one or a pratical one I agree) you CAN use it more than once a day. <BR><BR>
<BR><BR>
While under level 5 when you can die without end and not see Xp penalties this is VERY convinient. After that... you gotta weight out who you rather save the butt off, you or your other members...</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
